column5: Im looking for any info about Confusion Lake in northwest Ontario. Wilderness Air has a fly in cabin on this lake. If anyone has been there, it would be great to hear about it. https://www.wilderness-air-escapes.c...onfusion-lake/

Have guided on confusion for willderness air some years ago.the cabin wad great and have heard its a bit more modern now.fishing was great.there are lots of walleye.also we caught lake trout and northerns and some decent muskies also.dont think you could go wrong.
"Poultryman", now that was a great song. Phoebe Snow wasn't much to look at but she sure could sing. Sorry, couldn't help myself.
